their asses pretty bad.

94
00:06:00,235 --> 00:06:01,987
Dammit, it's not fair, man.

95
00:06:01,987 --> 00:06:04,698
That crazy bitch aims
for the balls every time!

96
00:06:04,698 --> 00:06:06,324
