97
00:06:06,324 --> 00:06:07,826
Protect our balls,
for starters.

98
00:06:07,826 --> 00:06:10,078
Come on, let's go ask Take.

99
00:06:10,078 --> 00:06:11,788
I'm sure Ikki's
worried about us,

100
00:06:11,788 --> 00:06:13,331
but it could be worse.

101
00:06:13,331 --> 00:06:15,792
On the bright side,
we managed to infiltrate

102
00:06:15,792 --> 00:06:17,294
