105
00:06:21,131 --> 00:06:27,971
♪

106
00:06:27,971 --> 00:06:30,015
I see; I was wondering
why he wasn't on

107
00:06:30,015 --> 00:06:33,143
the Maruvu G‐men's
most‐wanted list.

108
00:06:33,143 --> 00:06:34,686
What a bunch of bullshit.

109
00:06:34,686 --> 00:06:36,438
My Fang is crying.

110
00:06:36,438 --> 00:06:38,189
Fuck this!

111
00:06:38,189 --> 00:06:43,945
♪

112
00:06:43,945 --> 00:06:46,072
You punks just don't
know when to quit.

113
00:06:46,072 --> 00:06:47,490
The meeting time
was half an hour ago

114
00:06:47,490 --> 00:06:49,200
and we're still
missing five students.

115
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,327
Where did they go?

116
00:06:50,327 --> 00:06:51,244
This is
really bad,

117
00:06:51,244 --> 00:06:52,621
I can't find
them anywhere.

118
00:06:52,621 --> 00:06:54,748
Maybe you should report
this to the police!

119
00:06:54,748 --> 00:06:55,915
(exclaiming)

120
00:06:55,915 --> 00:06:57,208
No, if we do that,

121
00:06:57,208 --> 00:06:59,252
then we might have
to cancel the entire trip.

122
00:06:59,252 --> 00:07:00,420
I wouldn't wanna
ruin the memories

123
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:02,297
of all the other students
who have nothing to do

124
00:07:02,297 --> 00:07:03,548
with this mess.

125
00:07:03,548 --> 00:07:05,550
I'll take full
responsibility for them.

126
00:07:05,550 --> 00:07:08,553
For now, I suggest we keep
searching a little longer.

127
00:07:08,553 --> 00:07:10,221
That includes you three too.

128
00:07:10,221 --> 00:07:12,641
‐Now, get moving.
‐Yes, sir!

129
00:07:12,641 --> 00:07:15,143
(running footsteps)

130
00:07:15,143 --> 00:07:16,686
I hope Ikki can handle all this.

131
00:07:16,686 --> 00:07:18,772
I don't think I can
bring myself to tell him

132
00:07:18,772 --> 00:07:20,148
we all passed out.

133
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:21,900
Akito though look like he
was ready to kick some ass,

134
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:24,319
so it should be okay.

135
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:37,582
♪

136
00:07:37,582 --> 00:07:42,212
This is Trident's main base,
the Demons Trident 33.

137
00:07:42,212 --> 00:07:46,091
Now let's hope your friends
are still in one piece.

138
00:07:46,091 --> 00:07:48,093
It's way past the meeting time.

139
00:07:48,093 --> 00:07:49,511
What should we do?

140
00:07:49,511 --> 00:07:54,265
♪

141
00:07:54,265 --> 00:07:56,309
Huh?

142
00:07:56,309 --> 00:07:59,479
