143
00:07:59,479 --> 00:08:02,941
That's what I get for
using craptastic ATs.

144
00:08:02,941 --> 00:08:05,443
I hope you don't mind
but I got sick of waiting,

145
00:08:05,443 --> 00:08:07,946
